<para style="q1">

<verse number="4" style="v" />My life is among lions;</para>

<para style="q1">I am among those who are ready to devour me.</para>

<para style="q1">I am among people whose teeth are spears and arrows,</para>

<para style="q1">and whose tongues are sharp swords.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="5" style="v" />Be exalted, God, above the heavens;</para>

<para style="q1">let your glory be above all the earth.</para>

